WEBVTT

00:06.499 --> 00:07.840
(Respect copyright)

00:14.112 --> 00:20.704
♪Memories hold you back
from fulfilling your dreams♪

00:24.288 --> 00:30.432
♪Only by moving forward
can you find reunion♪

00:32.640 --> 00:35.872
♪Endings only mark new routes♪

00:36.096 --> 00:42.112
♪It's all part of the scenery♪

00:42.432 --> 00:45.856
♪To the horizon's call♪

00:45.920 --> 00:52.480
♪Your journey hasn't started♪

00:53.536 --> 00:57.472
♪Towards mountains,
chase the stars bright♪

00:57.472 --> 01:03.552
♪Let time embrace you
and wash away the past♪

01:03.840 --> 01:07.712
♪Put every twist behind you♪

01:07.712 --> 01:12.576
♪Drift leisurely through time♪

01:12.960 --> 01:15.680
♪Make headway against the wind♪

01:15.680 --> 01:18.667
♪Let mountains bow to your pace♪

01:18.720 --> 01:24.128
♪Rush towards a life without regret♪

01:24.640 --> 01:28.579
♪Let your nature burst free♪

01:30.240 --> 01:34.490
=The First Jasmine=

01:35.280 --> 01:37.776
=Episode 27=

01:38.130 --> 01:41.690
She previously bewitched my brother
into doing many bad things.

01:43.472 --> 01:45.050
Who exactly are you?

01:51.329 --> 01:52.249
Tianyi Pavilion.

01:55.410 --> 01:57.210
You're working for Mo Jingli?

01:57.529 --> 01:58.369
Prince Li?

02:01.050 --> 02:02.089
It can't be.

02:04.930 --> 02:07.529
After you fell off the cliff,
I was captured.

02:08.250 --> 02:09.810
They beat me up badly.

02:10.649 --> 02:13.209
Someone ordered them to skin me alive.

02:15.010 --> 02:16.850
But they didn't do so.

02:19.570 --> 02:23.130
Oh, they saw Tianyi Pavilion's mark
on me.

02:24.049 --> 02:27.489
They called him Your Highness.

02:28.090 --> 02:31.209
Where were you held at that time?

02:32.209 --> 02:35.370
In the southwestern capital outskirts,
not far from where you fell.

02:39.850 --> 02:42.370
Oh, there was a bamboo grove.

02:48.370 --> 02:49.489
Mo Jingli.

02:53.169 --> 02:56.810
With the death of Princess Lingyun,
Cangbei will surely be enraged.

02:57.769 --> 02:58.889
Peace will be hopeless.

03:00.090 --> 03:01.889
War might even break out immediately.

03:03.329 --> 03:06.010
They previously ordered Zhang Hengyuan
to kill Zhong Xingtong.

03:06.649 --> 03:08.290
That was meant to sow discord.

03:10.370 --> 03:11.329
Mo Jingli.

03:12.370 --> 03:14.810
Are you really going
to persist on the wrong path?

03:15.850 --> 03:17.810
Forget the peace or war for now.

03:18.049 --> 03:19.929
Let's first think about how to escape.

03:20.449 --> 03:23.290
Otherwise, we'll be the first
to lose our lives.

03:24.130 --> 03:24.970
My Lady.

03:27.929 --> 03:29.010
Don't be afraid.

03:29.929 --> 03:31.570
The killer is Su Zuidie.

03:31.690 --> 03:34.649
If we can find her,
there might be a way out.

03:37.649 --> 03:39.410
But we are trapped here.

03:39.609 --> 03:41.570
And His Highness is far away
from the capital.

03:44.690 --> 03:46.250
According to the law,

03:47.489 --> 03:50.704
prisoners should be provided with food,
clothing, and medical care, but if not,

03:50.970 --> 03:53.049
and if their families
are not allowed to visit,

03:53.690 --> 03:54.929
prison guards can be caned.

03:54.929 --> 03:57.530
What exactly do you mean?

04:01.329 --> 04:02.329
I mean,

04:03.250 --> 04:05.850
let me think about what to do.

04:45.810 --> 04:47.810
That guy seems off. Jin, go after him.

04:49.130 --> 04:51.610
Wang Suwu, you stay
and keep an eye on Chen Longxiang.

04:51.610 --> 04:52.250
Yes.

05:04.370 --> 05:06.610
Jingzhao Prefecture!
Halt for inspection!

05:33.089 --> 05:35.170
Prefect, we found this.

05:37.552 --> 05:40.240
(Princess Lingyun has been murdered
in Dachu. Report this to our lord.)

05:43.209 --> 05:46.769
(Princess Lingyun has been murdered
in Dachu. Report this to our lord.)

05:46.769 --> 05:48.329
How many messengers did you send out?

05:52.930 --> 05:53.730
What are you doing?

05:54.130 --> 05:56.409
Open your mouth!

05:56.849 --> 05:57.649
Spit it out!

06:03.930 --> 06:07.329
Your Highness, he had a poison capsule
hidden in his molar.

06:08.649 --> 06:09.570
He killed himself.

06:11.250 --> 06:12.769
What should we do next?

06:21.050 --> 06:22.930
No matter how many messengers they send

06:23.209 --> 06:25.409
to deliver a secret letter
from the capital to Cangbei,

06:25.769 --> 06:28.529
there are only two feasible
and covert routes.

06:28.969 --> 06:32.250
First, go north along the Yellow River,
a major waterway.

06:32.810 --> 06:34.209
This route saves some footwork.

06:34.209 --> 06:36.050
But it alternates
between water and land routes.

06:36.209 --> 06:38.010
They need reliable boatmen
to provide supplies.

06:38.610 --> 06:41.529
We have already intercepted this route.

06:41.730 --> 06:44.769
Second, make a detour to the northeast
and cross Mount Yan.

06:45.810 --> 06:47.969
This route is winding and circuitous.

06:48.409 --> 06:51.010
But precisely because it is remote,
people hardly think of it.

06:51.209 --> 06:54.570
If a messenger travels alone on a horse,
they will change horses and rest.

06:56.130 --> 06:56.930
Wang Suwu.

06:58.490 --> 07:00.610
Immediately take men to Mount Yan.

07:00.849 --> 07:01.649
Watch the mountain passes

07:01.649 --> 07:03.849
to prevent anyone
from delivering the message.

07:04.289 --> 07:05.170
Understood.

07:05.170 --> 07:07.250
Jin, send the order immediately.

07:07.250 --> 07:09.209
Activate our hidden spies
in the border regions

07:09.209 --> 07:10.209
and assist Wang Suwu.

07:10.209 --> 07:12.930
Strictly guard the several paths
near the mountain passes,

07:13.089 --> 07:14.610
and inspect anyone leaving the border.

07:15.250 --> 07:16.209
Understood.

07:17.610 --> 07:20.050
If even one message reaches Cangbei,

07:20.570 --> 07:22.010
disaster will loom.

07:22.930 --> 07:25.529
I entrust it to you two.

07:26.050 --> 07:26.849
- Yes.
- Yes.

07:30.209 --> 07:32.730
Your Highness, where are you going then?

07:33.130 --> 07:34.050
Returning to the capital.

07:35.649 --> 07:38.969
I have an idea that might get you out.

07:41.089 --> 07:42.409
As long as I plead guilty,

07:43.529 --> 07:44.849
they might release you, right?

07:45.570 --> 07:48.529
Han Mingxi, it's a capital crime.

07:51.649 --> 07:54.570
I owe you two lives, right?

07:55.329 --> 07:56.449
I'll pay with my life first.

08:01.769 --> 08:03.649
If my brother knew I was going to die,

08:04.250 --> 08:06.329
he would catch Su Zuidie
and exchange her for me.

08:08.250 --> 08:09.570
If he doesn't do so,

08:10.490 --> 08:13.130
I'll complain to our parents
after death.

08:14.089 --> 08:15.409
This case is of great importance.

08:16.089 --> 08:19.329
Without solid evidence,
they won't believe you.

08:20.250 --> 08:22.649
The top priority is to find Su Zuidie.

08:24.529 --> 08:27.370
Do you have any idea
where she might be hiding?

08:29.930 --> 08:31.409
I never meddled in their matters.

08:34.169 --> 08:36.560
Fine, you didn't before.

08:37.616 --> 08:38.672
And never meddle then.

08:55.929 --> 08:56.610
Come here.

09:00.929 --> 09:01.850
Turn around.

09:08.889 --> 09:11.210
Someone! Help!

09:11.529 --> 09:13.010
Princess Ding is vomiting blood!

09:17.210 --> 09:18.210
Go get the physician!

09:18.210 --> 09:18.769
Yes.

09:19.409 --> 09:20.210
It's...

09:20.210 --> 09:21.450
It's Zhenyu Poison.

09:21.970 --> 09:23.809
If I don't have the antidote
within four hours,

09:23.809 --> 09:25.289
I will die.

09:25.409 --> 09:26.929
An ordinary physician can't save me.

09:27.409 --> 09:30.130
Go find Gu Zheng. He has the antidote.

09:30.569 --> 09:32.769
Your Highness, what are you up to?

09:34.689 --> 09:35.250
Your Highness.

09:40.850 --> 09:42.370
According to the law,

09:43.610 --> 09:46.800
prisoners should be provided with food,
clothing, and medical care, but if not,

09:47.090 --> 09:49.072
and if their families
are not allowed to visit,

09:49.872 --> 09:51.024
prison guards can be caned.

09:51.090 --> 09:53.850
What exactly do you mean?

09:57.490 --> 09:58.370
I mean,

09:59.409 --> 10:01.889
let me think about what to do.

10:05.649 --> 10:07.689
Hurry up! If she dies here,

10:07.809 --> 10:09.130
you'll pay for that!

10:09.889 --> 10:11.289
Go quickly to Jingzhao Prefecture.

10:11.312 --> 10:14.224
(Jingzhao Prefecture)

10:14.490 --> 10:17.809
Have the messengers gone
to His Highness yet?

10:18.409 --> 10:19.370
As you instructed,

10:19.529 --> 10:21.529
two groups of men have gone separately.

10:22.970 --> 10:24.289
I hope it's not too late.

10:25.409 --> 10:27.970
Please wait a moment.
There will surely be news.

10:28.169 --> 10:29.370
You may go back to your work.

10:29.809 --> 10:30.490
Yes.

10:34.409 --> 10:35.130
Revenue Clerk Gu.

10:37.090 --> 10:38.289
Are you Revenue Clerk Gu Zheng?

10:40.130 --> 10:42.610
Sure, I am. Who are you?

10:43.569 --> 10:44.610
I am Li Feibai,

10:44.610 --> 10:46.010
a student of Zhu Yun at Lishan Academy,

10:46.250 --> 10:47.450
a schoolmate of Princess Ding.

10:47.649 --> 10:49.330
The steward of Shende Shop knows me.

10:49.490 --> 10:51.689
Right now, I have an urgent favor
to ask of you.

10:52.130 --> 10:53.250
What is it?

10:53.850 --> 10:55.529
I learned
that Ye Li has been imprisoned.

10:55.809 --> 10:57.889
Could you find a way to let me see her?

10:59.649 --> 11:01.169
I would like to help you.

11:01.169 --> 11:04.250
But at this very moment,
there is nothing I can do.

11:08.169 --> 11:10.649
Sir, an urgent report from the prison.

11:10.689 --> 11:13.450
They say Princess Ding vomited blood
and passed out.

11:14.090 --> 11:16.169
The Chief Imperial Secretary says
she was poisoned with Zhenyu Poison.

11:16.169 --> 11:17.730
She said you have the antidote.

11:17.730 --> 11:19.289
She needs the antidote right now.

11:19.889 --> 11:22.409
I have the antidote?

11:22.416 --> 11:24.432
(Prison)

11:32.289 --> 11:35.210
Your Highness, what exactly happened?

11:36.049 --> 11:37.010
I'm fine now.

11:38.049 --> 11:40.610
It's just a digestive pill?

11:42.169 --> 11:43.250
It works well, anyway.

11:43.929 --> 11:45.370
How is the situation now?

11:45.769 --> 11:48.490
Qingfeng Mingyue Tower has been closed
since Princess Lingyun died.

11:49.010 --> 11:50.409
No one is allowed to enter.

12:03.010 --> 12:03.970
What's wrong?

12:03.970 --> 12:07.049
Send someone to Cangbei's posthouse
and keep a close watch on Su Zuidie.

12:09.529 --> 12:13.289
Rest assured, I will find Prince Ding
as soon as possible.

12:15.490 --> 12:17.049
Thank you.

12:17.169 --> 12:19.289
I'm fine now. You can go back.

12:37.250 --> 12:38.970
Are you feeling better?

12:42.090 --> 12:45.250
You should know
how serious this case is.

12:45.850 --> 12:48.130
Princess Lingyun was assassinated,

12:48.250 --> 12:50.409
jeopardizing the relations
between the two nations.

12:50.689 --> 12:52.850
If we don't hand over the murderer
in three days,

12:53.330 --> 12:55.049
a war between Dachu and Cangbei

12:55.929 --> 12:57.370
will be unavoidable.

12:57.730 --> 12:59.610
Even if Prince Ding can rush back,

13:00.130 --> 13:02.010
I'm afraid it will be too late.

13:04.970 --> 13:08.409
Sir, I know the stakes of this case.

13:08.929 --> 13:10.569
But I did not kill Princess Lingyun.

13:12.010 --> 13:15.450
But currently, there is no evidence
in your favor, Your Highness.

13:16.610 --> 13:20.490
If you already have any clues,
could you tell me?

13:39.088 --> 13:41.648
(Marquis Muyang's Mansion)

13:51.970 --> 13:54.330
Marquis Muyang,
Su Zuidie requests an audience.

13:59.889 --> 14:00.490
Let her in.

14:00.850 --> 14:01.649
Yes.

14:10.250 --> 14:10.889
Everyone, leave.

14:11.850 --> 14:12.569
Yes.

14:21.169 --> 14:23.090
Marquis Muyang, you are in good spirits.

14:23.330 --> 14:24.610
Even at a time like this,

14:24.850 --> 14:27.569
you're still in the mood
for taking care of your plants.

14:36.210 --> 14:37.010
Who are you?

14:38.610 --> 14:39.850
Don't you recognize me?

14:41.569 --> 14:43.889
I know you're Princess Lingyun's maid.

14:44.809 --> 14:47.289
But now that the Princess
has been murdered,

14:47.569 --> 14:50.250
you shouldn't have come openly.

14:52.010 --> 14:54.090
So, who are you?

14:54.730 --> 14:55.730
What is your purpose?

14:56.450 --> 14:58.010
Who are you working for?

15:00.490 --> 15:02.610
It seems you truly don't recognize me.

15:03.169 --> 15:04.049
What a pity.

15:04.610 --> 15:07.689
They all say
I look very much like my father.

15:08.130 --> 15:11.929
Eight years ago,
in the great fire at the Eastern Palace,

15:12.450 --> 15:14.850
it was you who killed him
with your own hands.

15:18.130 --> 15:19.250
Don't you remember?

15:22.010 --> 15:23.450
You are from the Eastern Palace.

15:24.289 --> 15:26.689
So it was you
who killed Princess Lingyun.

15:27.569 --> 15:29.850
You want to provoke a war
between the two nations

15:29.850 --> 15:31.610
and benefit from that.

15:32.569 --> 15:35.569
Don't you know this is treason?

15:36.289 --> 15:37.850
Don't make it sound so harsh.

15:38.289 --> 15:41.649
Besides, when it comes to treason,

15:41.769 --> 15:44.610
how could we compare to
how far you have gone?

15:46.569 --> 15:48.450
Every year in March and September,

15:49.250 --> 15:52.850
the Zhou family in Huaixi
uses transporting supplies as a cover,

15:53.169 --> 15:54.850
secretly transporting military weapons

15:54.850 --> 15:57.730
to Cangbei through Suixue Pass.

15:58.569 --> 16:02.210
The winter before last,
under the pretext of disaster relief,

16:02.450 --> 16:05.689
you smuggled 500 mighty crossbows
out of the pass.

16:06.049 --> 16:09.450
The following year, you transported
eight Mountain Breaker crossbows.

16:10.049 --> 16:11.970
Cangbei's army has already mastered

16:11.970 --> 16:14.370
the manufacturing techniques
of these two types of crossbows.

16:14.610 --> 16:17.010
You've been a huge help to them.

16:17.809 --> 16:21.169
So, have you gained what you want
from them?

16:25.929 --> 16:29.409
Just get to the point.
What exactly do you want?

16:32.432 --> 16:34.049
You're a clever man.

16:34.769 --> 16:35.850
I'm here

16:36.169 --> 16:38.970
to present you with a big gift.

16:40.409 --> 16:40.929
What is it?

16:42.090 --> 16:43.210
A piece of news.

16:43.376 --> 16:45.649
Chen Longxiang has gone missing.

16:48.889 --> 16:49.970
So what?

16:50.010 --> 16:51.370
He faked his death to escape.

16:51.610 --> 16:55.049
For all these years,
he has been secretly working for you.

16:55.569 --> 16:58.010
He has escorted military equipment
to Cangbei several times.

16:58.649 --> 16:59.769
You tell me, Marquis Muyang,

17:00.090 --> 17:02.850
if Mo Xiuyao catches Chen Longxiang,

17:03.250 --> 17:06.010
with the noses of the hounds
of Jingzhao Prefecture,

17:06.410 --> 17:08.210
how many things will be dug up?

17:08.769 --> 17:10.650
Everything you have painstakingly built,

17:11.210 --> 17:12.849
including the lives
of your entire family,

17:13.890 --> 17:15.329
will all be destroyed.

17:17.930 --> 17:21.010
However, right now,
there is a perfect opportunity.

17:21.450 --> 17:23.049
Princess Lingyun is dead.

17:23.490 --> 17:26.809
All the evidence at the scene
points to Princess Ding.

17:27.210 --> 17:29.010
Cangbei's delegation is furious.

17:29.210 --> 17:31.849
The Empress Dowager and the Emperor
are in a terrible fix.

17:31.970 --> 17:34.609
They just want to give an explanation
as soon as possible

17:34.609 --> 17:36.210
to appease Cangbei's anger.

17:36.690 --> 17:39.609
This is a heaven-sent opportunity.

17:41.170 --> 17:42.250
What do you plan to do?

17:42.890 --> 17:43.769
What do I plan?

17:44.930 --> 17:47.730
Naturally, I want to take Ye Li down

17:47.970 --> 17:49.410
completely,

17:49.410 --> 17:51.650
get the entire Prince Ding's Mansion
into the mire,

17:52.010 --> 17:54.690
and make people believe
they murdered Princess Lingyun

17:54.690 --> 17:56.849
and provoked the war
between the two nations.

17:58.210 --> 17:59.690
Once Prince Ding's Mansion falls,

18:00.010 --> 18:01.450
Mo Xiuyao is doomed.

18:01.849 --> 18:04.849
Jingzhao Prefecture
will naturally collapse too.

18:05.329 --> 18:09.769
Who will have the time
to investigate the dead Chen Longxiang?

18:10.250 --> 18:13.730
Who will still keep hounding you?

18:19.450 --> 18:23.329
Marquis Muyang,
this is the best opportunity right now.

18:23.569 --> 18:26.089
It's also your only way
to save yourself.

18:29.329 --> 18:30.210
Otherwise,

18:30.928 --> 18:35.170
are you going to wait for Mo Xiuyao
to bring Chen Longxiang's confession

18:35.490 --> 18:38.329
and knock on the door of your mansion?

18:43.289 --> 18:46.096
It seems I really underestimated you.

18:53.569 --> 18:54.329
Jin.

18:55.930 --> 18:58.809
Is Princess Lingyun's death
really connected to Ye Li?

18:59.890 --> 19:01.170
What's your take?

19:02.170 --> 19:05.569
If I were to kill someone,
I'd never let myself be gravely injured

19:05.690 --> 19:07.650
and stay at the scene
waiting to be caught.

19:07.890 --> 19:10.250
Princess Ding doesn't
seem like such a foolish person.

19:11.890 --> 19:13.450
Don't you dislike her?

19:13.809 --> 19:15.089
Why are you speaking up for her?

19:16.769 --> 19:18.609
After all, she's Xu Wanzhou's daughter.

19:23.769 --> 19:27.329
Jin, I'm here today to bid farewell.

19:27.769 --> 19:29.809
Too many things have happened
in the capital.

19:30.289 --> 19:31.809
I am truly tired of it all.

19:32.609 --> 19:34.609
My father is old and frail.

19:35.410 --> 19:37.970
I've been away for many years,
unable to look after him.

19:38.210 --> 19:39.849
In his letters, he says he misses me.

19:40.170 --> 19:41.450
I want to go back and see him

19:41.849 --> 19:43.690
and also help him with the household.

19:45.450 --> 19:46.650
How long will you be gone?

19:48.849 --> 19:49.849
Not sure yet.

19:51.049 --> 19:52.849
My father has been in poor health.

19:53.410 --> 19:56.210
If he doesn't find me annoying
and thinks I can help,

19:56.410 --> 19:57.849
I will stay a bit longer.

19:59.010 --> 20:02.329
Anyway, you have people around you,
so I'm not worried.

20:06.809 --> 20:07.609
Go then.

20:11.849 --> 20:12.650
Shunxi.

20:15.210 --> 20:18.010
Prepare a pot of orchids
for the Dowager Consort.

20:18.450 --> 20:19.210
Yes.

20:24.250 --> 20:25.849
You have a long journey ahead.

20:26.529 --> 20:29.450
You can take the pot of flowers
as a keepsake.

20:33.250 --> 20:34.210
Thank you.

21:33.410 --> 21:34.450
Your Grace, wait.

21:42.410 --> 21:44.049
This is the orchid from Empress Dowager.

21:49.650 --> 21:50.450
Your Grace.

21:50.512 --> 21:54.369
(Danque Gate)

21:54.369 --> 21:57.690
Well, is Princess Ding the murderer?

22:01.769 --> 22:04.690
If the real murderer is found,
she will not be.

22:05.369 --> 22:09.129
Otherwise, she will
have to be the murderer.

22:13.210 --> 22:16.849
Inside these palace walls,
the truth never matters.

22:17.040 --> 22:21.170
(Danque Gate)

22:21.170 --> 22:24.010
Your Grace, will you return?

22:24.569 --> 22:25.809
The Empress Dowager will miss you.

22:28.049 --> 22:31.410
Look how well the wisteria
on these palace walls bloom.

22:31.849 --> 22:33.049
And who still remembers

22:34.089 --> 22:37.210
that when the late Emperor was alive,
it was crabapple flowers that bloomed?

22:40.650 --> 22:41.650
The same goes for people.

22:42.369 --> 22:45.769
Out with the old, in with the new.

23:10.256 --> 23:14.160
(Xiankun Miscellany, Volume 6)

23:30.849 --> 23:33.849
Your Grace, seven volumes
of Master Xiankun's posthumous works

23:34.049 --> 23:35.930
have been compiled and edited.

23:36.210 --> 23:38.450
Together with those not yet compiled,

23:38.809 --> 23:41.890
as well as manuscripts and loose pages
to be transcribed and collated,

23:41.970 --> 23:43.410
they filled 27 boxes.

23:44.049 --> 23:45.170
They are all here.

23:50.049 --> 23:50.849
Burn them.

24:50.129 --> 24:52.049
Marquis Muyang,
Dowager Consort Qin has left,

24:52.089 --> 24:53.210
with a huge entourage.

24:53.609 --> 24:56.250
Judging by the direction,
it seems she is returning to Nanyi.

25:00.769 --> 25:03.250
She is the beloved daughter
of Nanyi's lord.

25:04.010 --> 25:06.650
Her father rules three prefectures
and 18 counties in Lingnan,

25:07.010 --> 25:08.369
with heavy troops at hand.

25:09.410 --> 25:11.210
Naturally, she can leave
whenever she wants.

25:12.490 --> 25:14.329
But where can I go?

25:14.650 --> 25:16.410
You command widespread support
in the court.

25:16.769 --> 25:18.049
We all follow you.

25:22.490 --> 25:25.609
I deeply appreciate your loyalty.

25:27.609 --> 25:30.250
But throughout history,
when founding a dynasty,

25:31.210 --> 25:32.650
they all used ruthless officials

25:33.650 --> 25:35.049
to resolutely root out traitors

25:35.369 --> 25:38.210
and overhaul the court.

25:39.329 --> 25:42.970
However, they would burn bridges
in the end.

25:43.650 --> 25:46.849
Now, to protect the Emperor's throne,

25:47.769 --> 25:50.170
she has already regarded me
as a mortal threat.

25:51.010 --> 25:54.849
All these years, she has
promoted Yuan Fang and Gongshu Yang,

25:55.410 --> 25:58.569
precisely to weaken my power
step by step.

25:59.210 --> 26:00.569
When the time is right,

26:01.410 --> 26:02.849
she will eliminate me.

26:03.410 --> 26:04.049
Marquis Muyang.

26:05.970 --> 26:07.049
That woman is right.

26:07.849 --> 26:10.849
Princess Ding is the killer
of Princess Lingyun.

26:11.129 --> 26:12.569
If a war breaks out,

26:12.650 --> 26:15.010
no one will have time to target us.

26:15.490 --> 26:16.650
What are you trying to say?

26:16.809 --> 26:18.329
Prince Ding is plotting rebellion.

26:18.650 --> 26:19.809
Ye Li is the murderer.

26:20.210 --> 26:24.010
I'll make this an irrefutable case
at any cost.

26:37.129 --> 26:39.210
Go prepare the horses.

26:39.210 --> 26:41.569
Scour the entire city
and find Su Zuidie.

26:41.650 --> 26:42.289
- Yes.
- Yes.

26:42.289 --> 26:43.250
Go quickly!

26:48.250 --> 26:50.609
Sir, how is she?

26:51.250 --> 26:52.650
She is fine.

26:53.049 --> 26:56.170
She deliberately vomited blood
just to get an audience with me.

26:56.289 --> 26:58.369
Li knows martial arts.
How could she be easily framed?

26:58.809 --> 27:01.569
She said she doesn't know martial arts.

27:01.569 --> 27:03.930
Originally, Master Zhu could help her.

27:03.930 --> 27:07.490
But he went back to Lishan Mountain,
and now there is no one to help her.

27:07.569 --> 27:09.529
It's my fault. My fault.

27:20.010 --> 27:20.809
Where have you been?

27:25.809 --> 27:27.089
I just did what I had to do.

27:29.650 --> 27:32.210
That's my younger brother,
my only family.

27:32.849 --> 27:33.849
What else could I do?

27:34.089 --> 27:35.809
He should have been away from Ye Li.

27:37.049 --> 27:38.490
This is what our boss ordered.

27:38.890 --> 27:41.849
If we fail, both of us will die.

27:42.010 --> 27:44.089
Did he ever order you
to frame Princess Ding?

27:47.569 --> 27:49.089
This is the fastest way.

27:49.849 --> 27:53.609
Zuidie, you should know
there are some people you can't touch.

27:57.049 --> 27:59.970
Yes, you all have people you care about.

28:00.529 --> 28:01.690
But I don't.

28:02.609 --> 28:04.690
So I can do whatever I want.

28:05.410 --> 28:08.410
As long as I achieve my goal, I'm happy.

28:13.289 --> 28:14.690
I just went to see Marquis Muyang.

28:14.930 --> 28:16.769
He will find a way
to make Ye Li confess.

28:16.930 --> 28:19.010
Your brother will be fine.

28:30.289 --> 28:30.970
Halt!

28:31.849 --> 28:34.250
This is a restricted area.
No entry without permission.

28:34.250 --> 28:35.849
Fine, I know the rules.

28:46.224 --> 28:49.392
(Prison)

29:20.289 --> 29:21.968
Help!

29:23.210 --> 29:23.769
Ye Li.

29:23.890 --> 29:24.690
Someone!

29:30.849 --> 29:32.970
Help! Murder!

29:33.010 --> 29:35.529
Hit him! Don't you know martial arts?

29:35.529 --> 29:36.410
No, I don't.

29:36.410 --> 29:38.210
Help! Someone!

29:38.210 --> 29:39.170
Is anyone there?

30:04.369 --> 30:07.450
From now on, you'll be a regular worker
at Shende Shop.

30:16.569 --> 30:17.970
Your Highness, are you hurt?

30:20.210 --> 30:21.210
At a time like this,

30:22.089 --> 30:23.809
when the evidence is supposedly solid,

30:24.490 --> 30:27.450
who would try to infiltrate the prison
and assassinate me?

30:29.490 --> 30:31.250
I will definitely investigate this

30:32.089 --> 30:33.490
and give you an explanation.

30:35.529 --> 30:37.089
You are perceptive.

30:37.410 --> 30:38.490
You should understand

30:38.769 --> 30:41.129
that the crucial thing right now
is not my innocence.

30:41.289 --> 30:44.170
It's to find the real culprit
to prevent further harm to the nation.

30:48.049 --> 30:49.369
This case is of great importance.

30:49.849 --> 30:53.450
If I cannot clear my suspicion,
I have nowhere to run anyway.

31:09.769 --> 31:10.569
Who is it?

31:18.210 --> 31:21.569
He actually failed.
What a good-for-nothing.

31:23.289 --> 31:24.049
He?

31:25.730 --> 31:26.650
Who is he?

31:27.690 --> 31:29.609
Is it Marquis Muyang or Mo Jingli?

31:29.970 --> 31:31.210
Let me make a guess.

31:32.450 --> 31:33.650
In the first year of the Xide Era,

31:34.250 --> 31:36.450
your father was implicated
by the Eastern Palace and died.

31:37.210 --> 31:39.769
You and your sisters
were forced into exile in Luozhou.

31:40.569 --> 31:41.809
Two years later, in the summer,

31:42.250 --> 31:44.450
Cangbei broke through Luozhou.

31:44.650 --> 31:46.170
You were captured in the war.

31:47.010 --> 31:50.529
But strangely, your name was not
on the prisoner roster.

31:50.849 --> 31:53.769
No one in Cangbei's military camp
saw you either.

31:55.650 --> 31:57.529
But two years later, in early spring,

31:57.809 --> 32:00.809
you appeared at Cangbei's hunting ground
and became a slave.

32:01.609 --> 32:03.010
About four months later,

32:03.369 --> 32:06.569
Princess Lingyun encountered you
during a hunt.

32:06.690 --> 32:07.809
She kept you.

32:08.450 --> 32:10.329
Your whereabouts were unknown
for two years.

32:11.010 --> 32:14.289
I originally thought
you encountered unexpected difficulties.

32:14.529 --> 32:15.609
But it turns out

32:16.250 --> 32:18.129
you were saved
by remnants of the Eastern Palace

32:18.569 --> 32:19.849
and planted in Cangbei.

32:20.769 --> 32:24.289
You assassinated Princess Lingyun
to start a war between the two nations

32:24.289 --> 32:25.849
and benefit from that.

32:26.529 --> 32:29.569
You act by the order of Mo Jingli.

32:33.329 --> 32:35.650
As for why Marquis Muyang is involved,

32:36.049 --> 32:37.569
and even sent someone to kill me,

32:38.289 --> 32:40.210
it's because of the weaponry case.

32:40.569 --> 32:42.569
He colluded
with the former Cangbei forces.

32:44.369 --> 32:45.329
Very clever of you.

32:45.730 --> 32:48.410
Unfortunately, you realized too late.

32:49.769 --> 32:51.170
Why did you do this?

32:53.490 --> 32:55.930
Guo Jin caused countless deaths
in the Eastern Palace.

32:56.529 --> 32:58.569
I must make her pay.

32:59.450 --> 33:00.650
Once Lingyun is dead,

33:01.210 --> 33:03.450
Dachu and Cangbei
will inevitably go to war.

33:03.809 --> 33:06.849
I want to make them desperate.

33:07.250 --> 33:10.690
I want to make them pay the price.

33:11.730 --> 33:14.129
The Eastern Palace lost
in the power struggle.

33:14.369 --> 33:16.329
I understand your desire for revenge.

33:16.769 --> 33:18.569
But why drag me into this?

33:20.890 --> 33:21.970
You don't understand?

33:30.410 --> 33:33.210
Because of Mo Xiuyao?

33:43.129 --> 33:44.490
I was exiled for 3,000 li.

33:45.369 --> 33:46.930
Setting off every day at the Chen hour,

33:47.529 --> 33:48.970
and only stopping at the You hour.

33:49.849 --> 33:53.569
If we walked a bit slower,
we would be whipped.

33:56.450 --> 33:58.049
Later, when we arrived in Luozhou,

33:58.769 --> 34:00.730
we still had to wear shackles every day

34:01.609 --> 34:03.769
and wash clothes by the cold river.

34:05.010 --> 34:06.490
One day in winter,

34:07.210 --> 34:08.770
I couldn't take it anymore.

34:09.649 --> 34:12.450
I tried to escape, but was discovered.

34:13.010 --> 34:14.689
They locked me in the woodshed.

34:15.169 --> 34:16.930
They burned me with red-hot iron.

34:17.810 --> 34:21.049
At that time,
I prayed every day that someone

34:21.609 --> 34:22.672
would come save me.

34:23.209 --> 34:24.169
But what about him?

34:24.930 --> 34:26.290
I was betrothed to him.

34:27.049 --> 34:29.330
But he was living comfortably at home.

34:31.290 --> 34:32.770
Mo Xiuyao didn't have it easy either.

34:35.249 --> 34:38.569
His elder brother was killed,
and the Heiyun Cavalry was disbanded.

34:39.089 --> 34:42.089
He had just won a battle
when he was hauled back to the capital.

34:43.169 --> 34:45.089
Later, he was finally released.

34:45.209 --> 34:46.529
And his title was restored.

34:47.770 --> 34:51.370
But he could never stand again.

34:52.049 --> 34:53.529
He was also a victim.

34:54.810 --> 34:55.850
A victim?

34:56.970 --> 34:58.290
He deserved it.

34:59.169 --> 35:02.569
He betrayed me
and the late Crown Prince.

35:03.689 --> 35:07.249
Since he is willing
to be Guo Jin's lackey,

35:07.569 --> 35:08.930
you both deserve to die.

35:09.529 --> 35:12.930
Now, you're simply
reaping what you sowed.

35:13.450 --> 35:15.330
You deserve this.

35:16.770 --> 35:17.850
You've all heard it.

35:26.290 --> 35:28.930
Sir, you know the truth now.

35:30.410 --> 35:31.770
Thank you.

35:37.200 --> 35:38.410
(Yaohua Garden)

35:38.410 --> 35:39.209
Father.

35:40.529 --> 35:41.609
What are you doing here?

35:42.129 --> 35:43.529
Didn't I tell you to leave here?

35:44.529 --> 35:45.890
The Empress Dowager brought me back.

35:46.129 --> 35:48.649
She was bored in the palace
and asked me to keep her company.

35:48.850 --> 35:51.529
Father, guess what?
The Empress Dowager really likes me.

35:51.649 --> 35:54.450
She said that with me around,
the palace became much livelier.

35:54.490 --> 35:56.049
She even has a better appetite.

36:04.770 --> 36:07.049
Father, what's wrong?

36:09.209 --> 36:10.010
Nothing.

36:10.490 --> 36:11.290
Tianyang.

36:13.089 --> 36:15.649
Find an opportunity
to implore the Empress Dowager

36:16.689 --> 36:18.410
to allow you to return
to Lingnan sooner.

36:19.209 --> 36:22.209
Your mom has written in to say
she has been unwell recently.

36:23.410 --> 36:25.689
What? How could Mom be unwell?

36:25.689 --> 36:27.290
Father, is Mom ill?

36:27.290 --> 36:28.169
- What's wrong?
- Tianyang.

36:29.089 --> 36:29.970
Don't worry.

36:30.370 --> 36:32.850
Perhaps she just misses you terribly.

36:36.169 --> 36:38.810
You're likable and well-behaved.

36:39.609 --> 36:40.930
When you speak to the Empress Dowager,

36:42.249 --> 36:43.529
watch your attitude.

36:44.249 --> 36:45.689
Don't disobey her.

36:47.930 --> 36:50.330
Don't worry, Father. I understand.

36:50.770 --> 36:53.729
Father, you should also talk more
with the Empress Dowager.

36:53.850 --> 36:56.529
Perhaps because Sister Qin left,
she's in a bad mood.

36:58.850 --> 36:59.930
I see.

37:00.770 --> 37:04.049
Father, I'll go to the garden
and pick some flowers.

37:04.609 --> 37:05.529
I take my leave.

37:29.850 --> 37:30.410
(Jin.)

37:31.770 --> 37:33.330
I'm here today to bid farewell.

37:33.770 --> 37:35.810
Too many things have happened
in the capital.

37:36.290 --> 37:37.569
I am truly tired of it all.

37:39.609 --> 37:41.370
You're in a very high position,

37:42.890 --> 37:45.129
as bright as the sunshine.

37:45.770 --> 37:46.770
Your hands are clean.

37:47.649 --> 37:49.010
But what about my hands?

37:50.689 --> 37:52.450
My hands got dirty

37:53.290 --> 37:54.609
with blood.

37:54.689 --> 37:56.649
Back then,
I helped you handle so many things.

37:57.810 --> 38:00.330
Now, times have changed.

38:00.729 --> 38:03.330
So, you want to wipe it all clean?

38:09.370 --> 38:10.129
Shunxi.

38:12.169 --> 38:13.936
Well, the sun

38:13.936 --> 38:14.770
(Anqing Palace)

38:14.770 --> 38:16.850
from yesterday and the day before

38:17.370 --> 38:20.689
was the same as the one
from ten years ago?

38:21.490 --> 38:23.129
Isn't it still the same sun?

38:23.770 --> 38:27.209
I'm confused.
To me, it looks as bright as ever.

38:30.209 --> 38:33.529
Then, are you the same

38:33.810 --> 38:34.930
as yesterday?

38:36.209 --> 38:37.970
I'm who I am,

38:38.010 --> 38:40.930
the one who always serves you.

38:43.410 --> 38:46.209
When you combed your hair this morning,
did some hair fall out?

38:47.209 --> 38:50.609
Hair? It did fall out.

38:53.370 --> 38:56.049
A hair strand leaves its root,
like withered grass.

38:57.129 --> 38:59.970
Our body constantly changes.

39:00.850 --> 39:02.209
Yesterday's Shunxi

39:02.850 --> 39:06.169
has already passed away
along with that fallen hair.

39:08.049 --> 39:11.010
Your Majesty,
your words are too profound.

39:11.010 --> 39:12.450
I feel a bit uneasy hearing them.

39:20.089 --> 39:21.008
It's time for court.

39:21.040 --> 39:22.384
(Anqing Palace)

39:27.120 --> 39:31.440
(Lasting Brilliance)

39:35.609 --> 39:37.729
Your Majesties.

39:38.169 --> 39:40.450
Su Zuidie has already confessed.

39:40.810 --> 39:42.450
Out of old grudges,

39:42.490 --> 39:45.010
she deliberately plotted
to poison Princess Lingyun.

39:45.010 --> 39:46.890
And then, she framed Princess Ding.

39:47.010 --> 39:47.970
Her purpose

39:48.010 --> 39:51.129
was to provoke a conflict
between Dachu and Cangbei.

39:51.609 --> 39:53.089
That's quite outrageous.

40:04.410 --> 40:08.049
We recklessly fell into her trick,

40:08.490 --> 40:10.089
nearly causing a great disaster.

40:10.410 --> 40:12.810
Previously, we were very offensive.

40:13.609 --> 40:17.450
We beg Your Majesties for forgiveness.

40:18.049 --> 40:19.330
General Lei, please rise.

40:23.010 --> 40:25.729
You seek justice for your master
out of loyalty.

40:26.490 --> 40:29.490
We will certainly not blame you.

40:29.890 --> 40:31.970
Also, Su Zuidie

40:32.290 --> 40:34.810
is the maid of Princess Lingyun.

40:34.850 --> 40:36.209
She is a person of Cangbei.

40:36.649 --> 40:38.930
Therefore, this case

40:39.049 --> 40:41.569
should be fully adjudicated by Cangbei.

40:41.689 --> 40:43.810
Dachu will not meddle further.

40:44.450 --> 40:46.930
So, General Lei,
you may take the criminal back

40:47.010 --> 40:48.529
and tell your lord the truth

40:48.609 --> 40:51.370
in full detail.

40:51.770 --> 40:54.890
Hope our two nations will make peace.
That would be a blessing.

40:55.049 --> 40:56.970
Very wise decision, Your Majesty.

40:57.729 --> 40:59.370
I will keep this in my mind

40:59.649 --> 41:01.330
and tell our lord the truth

41:01.370 --> 41:03.810
in full detail.

41:07.490 --> 41:08.290
I'll take my leave.

41:19.010 --> 41:21.770
Princess Ding,
do you have anything else to say

41:21.850 --> 41:23.890
in the court?

41:26.770 --> 41:28.850
Your Majesties.

41:29.569 --> 41:33.089
I'll accuse Zhou Jing, Chief Minister
of Imperial Court of Judicial Review.

41:33.370 --> 41:36.209
I accuse him
of attempting to silence me.

41:39.649 --> 41:41.930
Princess Ding, rise and speak.

41:43.209 --> 41:44.129
Thanks, Your Majesty.

41:48.850 --> 41:50.930
May it please Your Majesties,

41:51.810 --> 41:54.729
Marquis Muyang has a henchman
named Zhao Ting.

41:55.089 --> 41:57.770
Last night, Zhao Ting,
holding a sharp blade,

41:57.890 --> 42:00.330
infiltrated the prison
and attempted to assassinate me.

42:00.770 --> 42:03.370
That's quite outrageous.

42:03.810 --> 42:06.049
He treats the law as nothing.

42:12.330 --> 42:13.689
What Princess Ding said

42:13.850 --> 42:16.529
reminds me of something suspicious.

42:16.810 --> 42:19.729
A few days ago, Marquis Muyang's man,
Zhang Hengyuan,

42:20.209 --> 42:22.129
attempted to assassinate Zhong Xingtong.

42:22.770 --> 42:24.689
Last night, his henchman, Zhao Ting,

42:25.249 --> 42:26.890
attempted to assassinate Princess Ding.

42:27.129 --> 42:30.010
Such two shocking assassination cases.

42:30.249 --> 42:32.810
Their masterminds
are both close followers

42:33.209 --> 42:36.209
of Marquis Muyang.

42:36.410 --> 42:38.649
Isn't this far too coincidental?

42:38.736 --> 42:41.520
(Preview)

42:42.569 --> 42:44.930
This is the late Emperor's handwriting
and seal.

42:45.330 --> 42:47.810
A comparison will reveal the truth.

42:48.290 --> 42:50.729
Zhou Jing, what else do you have to say?

42:51.209 --> 42:54.169
Please allow me to submit a petition.

42:54.529 --> 42:57.129
My Lady, I'm scared.

42:57.569 --> 43:00.169
But if we don't tell him, he won't know.

43:00.649 --> 43:03.209
The truth is the truth.
It can't be hidden.

43:03.410 --> 43:05.810
(Auspicious)
If I had told her fortune at that time,

43:06.049 --> 43:08.010
would she have been spared from death?

43:14.736 --> 43:21.328
♪Memories hold you back
from fulfilling your dreams♪

43:24.912 --> 43:31.056
♪Only by moving forward
can you find reunion♪

43:33.264 --> 43:36.496
♪Endings only mark new routes♪

43:36.720 --> 43:42.736
♪It's all part of the scenery♪

43:43.056 --> 43:46.480
♪To the horizon's call♪

43:46.544 --> 43:53.104
♪Your journey hasn't started♪

43:54.160 --> 43:58.096
♪Towards mountains,
chase the stars bright♪

43:58.096 --> 44:03.792
♪Both joy and grief
make the trip worthwhile♪

44:04.304 --> 44:12.912
♪Trying to catch up
to your own lost shadow♪

44:13.808 --> 44:19.312
♪Within the wilds, echoes thrive♪

44:19.312 --> 44:24.816
♪Clear mind leads to a clear path♪

44:24.880 --> 44:28.944
♪Be grateful to your losses♪

44:29.232 --> 44:34.456
♪Make your steps weightless♪

44:35.056 --> 44:38.768
♪Towards mountains,
chase the stars bright♪

44:38.800 --> 44:44.464
♪Let time embrace you
and wash away the past♪

44:45.232 --> 44:53.200
♪Put every twist behind you,
drift leisurely through time♪

44:54.608 --> 44:59.856
♪Make headway against the wind,
let mountains bow to your pace♪

45:00.112 --> 45:06.016
♪Rush towards a life without regret♪

45:06.016 --> 45:10.136
♪Let your nature burst free♪

45:10.352 --> 45:15.088
♪Unbound by form♪

45:16.304 --> 45:20.576
♪Let your nature burst free♪

45:20.816 --> 45:26.256
♪Unbound by form♪
